00:00:26.943 --> 00:00:28.737 position:50% align:center
Oh, I hope your band does well.

00:00:28.820 --> 00:00:30.488 position:50% align:center
[ASUMI, TAEKO, HIDEKI gasp]

00:00:30.572 --> 00:00:32.115 position:50% align:center
