00:00:34.951 --> 00:00:36.369 position:50% align:center
[TAEKO, HIDEKI chuckle]

00:00:36.453 --> 00:00:37.787 position:50% align:center
I gotta go.

00:00:37.871 --> 00:00:39.789 position:50% align:center
[GROUP]
Good luck out there!

00:02:29.274 --> 00:02:31.985 position:50% align:center
[CHINU grunting]

00:02:35.739 --> 00:02:36.990 position:50% align:center
[GROUP]
Yeah!

00:02:37.073 --> 00:02:37.866 position:50% align:center
Yeah!

00:02:37.949 --> 00:02:40.076 position:50% align:center
That shot was perfect, Chinu!

00:02:42.829 --> 00:02:45.707 position:50% align:center
Well, today's the day
you've been practicing for!

00:02:45.790 --> 00:02:48.251 position:50% align:center
Not that I've been there.

00:02:48.335 --> 00:02:51.254 position:50% align:center
Anyway, get out there
and make some touchdowns!

00:02:51.338 --> 00:02:54.549 position:50% align:center
Or "polos," however
you score in this.

00:02:54.632 --> 00:02:56.801 position:50% align:center
I don't know!

00:02:56.885 --> 00:02:58.636 position:50% align:center
[GROUP]
Right.

00:02:58.720 --> 00:03:00.972 position:50% align:center
I'll learn the rules
during the match.

00:03:02.599 --> 00:03:04.017 position:50% align:center
Man, what a crappy speech.

00:03:04.100 --> 00:03:05.518 position:50% align:center
Hey, he's trying his best.

00:03:05.602 --> 00:03:06.936 position:50% align:center
Is he really, though?

00:03:07.020 --> 00:03:08.188 position:50% align:center
Well then, Babi!

00:03:08.271 --> 00:03:10.398 position:50% align:center
Did you happen to bring
any chocolate today?

00:03:10.482 --> 00:03:11.775 position:50% align:center
[EITARO, YOSHIHARU gsp]

00:03:11.858 --> 00:03:14.069 position:50% align:center
Yeah, I did, but...

00:03:15.236 --> 00:03:17.906 position:50% align:center
You go ahead.
I don't want any, though.

00:03:17.989 --> 00:03:19.657 position:50% align:center
[BABAYARO grunts]

00:03:19.741 --> 00:03:20.992 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
More importantly, Captain!

00:03:21.076 --> 00:03:22.327 position:50% align:center
[JO]
Hm?

00:03:22.410 --> 00:03:24.496 position:50% align:center
Are you ever gonna explain
to me how this happened?

00:03:24.579 --> 00:03:26.873 position:50% align:center
We look like idiots
wearing these damn things!

00:03:26.956 --> 00:03:28.208 position:50% align:center
There was a slight mix up,

00:03:28.291 --> 00:03:29.668 position:50% align:center
but we already lived
through that drama.

00:03:29.751 --> 00:03:30.502 position:50% align:center
[GROUP grunts]

00:03:30.585 --> 00:03:31.836 position:50% align:center
[MINATO growls]

00:03:31.920 --> 00:03:33.755 position:50% align:center
[TAKESHI] Hey, you guys
are lookin' pretty snazzy

00:03:33.838 --> 00:03:35.757 position:50% align:center
in those warmups!

00:03:36.758 --> 00:03:37.967 position:50% align:center
Since you play like crap,

00:03:38.051 --> 00:03:39.719 position:50% align:center
it makes sense you'd
look like it, too.

00:03:39.803 --> 00:03:40.720 position:50% align:center
What?

00:03:40.804 --> 00:03:42.305 position:50% align:center
[NORIMICHI]
Cut it out, Toyama.

00:03:42.389 --> 00:03:45.058 position:50% align:center
[AKIHISA] We just wanted to
stop by and wish you good luck.

00:03:45.141 --> 00:03:46.559 position:50% align:center
Right back 'atcha.

00:03:46.643 --> 00:03:49.312 position:50% align:center
One of our teams will
have its first victory today.

00:03:49.396 --> 00:03:52.315 position:50% align:center
And if those getups are
any indication, it'll be us.

00:03:52.399 --> 00:03:53.316 position:50% align:center
What'd you say?

00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:54.901 position:50% align:center
--[MINATO] Hey!
--[TAKESHI] Huh?

00:03:55.902 --> 00:03:58.154 position:50% align:center
You talk pretty big
for a bunch of wimps.

00:03:58.238 --> 00:03:59.823 position:50% align:center
You forget what
happened in middle school?

00:03:59.906 --> 00:04:02.409 position:50% align:center
I scored ten points on you
and you ran home crying.

00:04:02.492 --> 00:04:04.244 position:50% align:center
[GROUP gasps]

00:04:04.327 --> 00:04:05.537 position:50% align:center
You remember that?

00:04:05.620 --> 00:04:07.664 position:50% align:center
Oh, I remember everything.

00:04:08.998 --> 00:04:11.042 position:50% align:center
[TAKESHI] Yeah, well, we've
gotten way stronger since then.

00:04:11.126 --> 00:04:12.836 position:50% align:center
Yeah?

00:04:12.919 --> 00:04:15.755 position:50% align:center
These losers aren't half
as good as your old team.

00:04:15.839 --> 00:04:17.924 position:50% align:center
We're not afraid of you!

00:04:19.092 --> 00:04:21.928 position:50% align:center
[GROUP grunts]

00:04:22.012 --> 00:04:23.555 position:50% align:center
[AKIHISA]
See you in the pool.

00:04:49.914 --> 00:04:52.500 position:50% align:center
[MINATO] Hey. You really
wear that for games?

00:04:52.584 --> 00:04:54.044 position:50% align:center
Yeah.

00:04:55.378 --> 00:04:58.298 position:50% align:center
[MINATO] His range of motion's
gotta be terrible in those.

00:04:58.381 --> 00:05:00.508 position:50% align:center
This is gonna be
worse than I thought.

00:05:00.592 --> 00:05:02.552 position:50% align:center
I'll have to step it up
if we want to--

00:05:02.635 --> 00:05:03.762 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:05:10.560 --> 00:05:12.812 position:50% align:center
[CHINU] Looking forward
to watching you play.

00:05:29.079 --> 00:05:31.456 position:50% align:center
So how long is
a match, exactly?

00:05:31.539 --> 00:05:33.500 position:50% align:center
Every match consists
of four periods

00:05:33.583 --> 00:05:35.043 position:50% align:center
that are each
eight minutes long.

00:05:35.126 --> 00:05:37.212 position:50% align:center
[MITAMURA] Oh, so we'll
be done in half an hour?

00:05:37.295 --> 00:05:39.214 position:50% align:center
[EITARO] No. Every
time there's a foul,

00:05:39.297 --> 00:05:40.548 position:50% align:center
they have to stop the clock

00:05:40.632 --> 00:05:43.176 position:50% align:center
and there's no telling
how many might be called.

00:05:43.259 --> 00:05:45.178 position:50% align:center
To resume the game,
you have to pass.

00:05:45.261 --> 00:05:46.554 position:50% align:center
You aren't allowed
to take a shot.

00:05:46.638 --> 00:05:48.139 position:50% align:center
And all that
stopping and starting?

00:05:48.223 --> 00:05:50.225 position:50% align:center
Yeah, it adds up way
quicker than you'd think.

00:05:50.308 --> 00:05:53.228 position:50% align:center
So really, each period is
more like fifteen minutes.

00:05:53.311 --> 00:05:54.688 position:50% align:center
After the first
and third periods,

00:05:54.771 --> 00:05:56.481 position:50% align:center
there's a two-minute
break to rest.

00:05:56.564 --> 00:05:59.109 position:50% align:center
Oh, we also take a 15-minute
break during halftime.

00:05:59.192 --> 00:06:01.444 position:50% align:center
So normally,
it lasts around an hour.

00:06:01.528 --> 00:06:03.780 position:50% align:center
Your feet can't touch
the bottom for a whole hour?

00:06:03.863 --> 00:06:05.031 position:50% align:center
Ooh, that's a workout.

00:06:05.115 --> 00:06:06.408 position:50% align:center
Yeah...

00:06:10.203 --> 00:06:11.871 position:50% align:center
[EITARO]
Sorry, coming!

00:06:14.541 --> 00:06:16.876 position:50% align:center
[KEITA]
This time, Minato is our enemy.

00:06:16.960 --> 00:06:18.670 position:50% align:center
So, no cheering for him,
understand?

00:06:18.753 --> 00:06:20.630 position:50% align:center
Yeah, yeah, I know.

00:06:34.436 --> 00:06:36.730 position:50% align:center
[MINATO] Okay, looks like
they've set up haircut

00:06:36.813 --> 00:06:39.691 position:50% align:center
over there to be their sprinter.

00:06:39.774 --> 00:06:41.860 position:50% align:center
We're counting on you, Amihama.

00:06:46.865 --> 00:06:49.492 position:50% align:center
[TAKESHI grunting]

00:06:52.620 --> 00:06:54.914 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO grunts]

00:06:54.998 --> 00:06:56.708 position:50% align:center
[EITARO]
Off to a good start!

00:06:56.791 --> 00:06:59.210 position:50% align:center
Now, it's up to me to
get the ball to Minato!

00:06:59.294 --> 00:07:00.462 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:07:02.339 --> 00:07:03.923 position:50% align:center
[EITARO]
They put six players on him?!

00:07:04.007 --> 00:07:05.508 position:50% align:center
[GROUP grunts]

00:07:05.592 --> 00:07:07.844 position:50% align:center
[TAKESHI] We saw you planning
your strategy around Kiyomizu.

00:07:07.927 --> 00:07:09.387 position:50% align:center
So, we did, too!

00:07:09.471 --> 00:07:12.474 position:50% align:center
[AKIHISA] If we shut him down,
we'll have nothing to fear!

00:07:12.557 --> 00:07:14.434 position:50% align:center
--[NORIMICHI chuckles]
--[MINATO grunts]

00:07:14.517 --> 00:07:16.853 position:50% align:center
[EITARO grunts]

00:07:20.482 --> 00:07:23.068 position:50% align:center
[MITAMURA] Okay. Once the ball
is in your team's possession,

00:07:23.151 --> 00:07:25.612 position:50% align:center
you have 30 seconds to shoot.

00:07:25.695 --> 00:07:27.906 position:50% align:center
How much time is left?

00:07:27.989 --> 00:07:29.324 position:50% align:center
Five seconds?!

00:07:29.407 --> 00:07:30.533 position:50% align:center
[BABAYARO grunts]

00:07:33.495 --> 00:07:34.245 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
Chase him!

00:07:34.329 --> 00:07:36.915 position:50% align:center
[YOSHIHARU grunts]

00:07:38.124 --> 00:07:39.501 position:50% align:center
Already?

00:07:42.003 --> 00:07:43.588 position:50% align:center
[NORIMICHI grunts]

00:07:48.051 --> 00:07:49.886 position:50% align:center
[JO]
You're not getting past me!

00:07:55.183 --> 00:07:57.435 position:50% align:center
[whistle blows]

00:08:08.196 --> 00:08:10.073 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
I've gotta do something!

00:08:13.660 --> 00:08:15.537 position:50% align:center
[MINATO grunts]

00:08:17.622 --> 00:08:20.041 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
C'mon! Pass!

00:08:20.125 --> 00:08:22.544 position:50% align:center
[MINATO grunts]
Pass to me!

00:08:25.630 --> 00:08:28.550 position:50% align:center
[BABAYARO]
Um... Who should I pass to?

00:08:28.633 --> 00:08:30.010 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:08:39.686 --> 00:08:41.021 position:50% align:center
[TAKESHI grunts]

00:08:41.104 --> 00:08:42.939 position:50% align:center
[yells]

00:08:45.525 --> 00:08:47.277 position:50% align:center
[whistle blows]

00:08:47.360 --> 00:08:48.820 position:50% align:center
[NORIMICHI chuckles]

00:08:51.114 --> 00:08:52.741 position:50% align:center
[MINATO growls]

00:08:56.661 --> 00:08:57.912 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
What was that all about?

00:08:57.996 --> 00:08:59.998 position:50% align:center
Let me focus on the attack.

00:09:00.081 --> 00:09:01.666 position:50% align:center
You guys stick to
countering, you got it?

00:09:01.750 --> 00:09:03.168 position:50% align:center
--[TAKEKAZU] On it!
--[GROUP] Right!

00:09:03.251 --> 00:09:04.419 position:50% align:center
Hey, Ushimado.

00:09:04.502 --> 00:09:07.213 position:50% align:center
I think you and I should
swap who we're guarding.

00:09:07.297 --> 00:09:09.966 position:50% align:center
Right now, it's you up
against their fastest swimmer.

00:09:10.050 --> 00:09:11.259 position:50% align:center
[YOSHIHARU]
Mm...

00:09:12.635 --> 00:09:13.970 position:50% align:center
[TAKESHI chuckles]

00:09:18.975 --> 00:09:20.101 position:50% align:center
[MITAMURA]
Oh, dear.

00:09:20.185 --> 00:09:22.520 position:50% align:center
It's the second half
and we're still behind.

00:09:24.439 --> 00:09:26.900 position:50% align:center
[KOKI] It was smart of them
to put your brother on Toyama.

00:09:26.983 --> 00:09:29.611 position:50% align:center
That's stopped Rikka
from scoring, but...

00:09:29.694 --> 00:09:33.615 position:50% align:center
Yamanami doesn't seem able to
put any points on the board.

00:09:33.698 --> 00:09:35.283 position:50% align:center
[MOMO]
Get it together, Minato.

00:09:35.367 --> 00:09:37.369 position:50% align:center
At this rate, you're gonna lose.

00:09:39.537 --> 00:09:41.539 position:50% align:center
[AKIHISA, MINATO grunting]

00:09:41.623 --> 00:09:42.791 position:50% align:center
[MINATO] C'mon!

00:09:42.874 --> 00:09:44.834 position:50% align:center
We have to defend this
and counter their play!

00:09:44.918 --> 00:09:46.378 position:50% align:center
[AKIHISA grunts]

00:09:46.461 --> 00:09:48.046 position:50% align:center
[TAKESHI grunts]

00:09:48.588 --> 00:09:51.049 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO]
Think you can outswim me?

00:09:51.132 --> 00:09:52.133 position:50% align:center
[SHUGO grunts]

00:09:52.217 --> 00:09:55.011 position:50% align:center
[MINATO gasps]
He blocked off Amihama!

00:09:55.095 --> 00:09:56.888 position:50% align:center
It's a pick!

00:09:56.971 --> 00:09:58.807 position:50% align:center
Huh? Huh?

00:09:58.890 --> 00:10:00.266 position:50% align:center
Ah...

00:10:03.144 --> 00:10:04.646 position:50% align:center
[TAKESHI grunts]

00:10:04.729 --> 00:10:05.855 position:50% align:center
[JO shouts]

00:10:05.939 --> 00:10:08.441 position:50% align:center
--[whistle blows]
--[MINATO growls]

00:10:14.989 --> 00:10:17.033 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
Ugh! Right in my space!

00:10:17.117 --> 00:10:18.368 position:50% align:center
Get the hell off!

00:10:18.451 --> 00:10:20.120 position:50% align:center
[whistle blows]

00:10:20.203 --> 00:10:21.246 position:50% align:center
[MINATO gasps]

00:10:21.329 --> 00:10:21.705 position:50% align:center
[RIKKA GAKUEN POLO PLAYERS]
Our ball!

00:10:21.788 --> 00:10:23.581 position:50% align:center
Shit!

00:10:23.665 --> 00:10:26.418 position:50% align:center
Oh, no, what happened?
Did we foul someone?

00:10:26.501 --> 00:10:27.836 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:10:32.966 --> 00:10:35.051 position:50% align:center
[JO grunts]

00:10:35.135 --> 00:10:37.345 position:50% align:center
[whistle blows]

00:10:38.555 --> 00:10:40.724 position:50% align:center
Boy, oh, boy, oh, boy.

00:10:46.021 --> 00:10:47.772 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
Dammit.

00:10:47.856 --> 00:10:50.442 position:50% align:center
If they pull ahead any
further we're done for.

00:10:50.525 --> 00:10:52.777 position:50% align:center
[EITARO]
Can I try passing to you?

00:10:52.861 --> 00:10:55.697 position:50% align:center
[MINATO] Huh? And where
exactly would you aim?

00:10:55.780 --> 00:10:57.157 position:50% align:center
They've been swarming me
the whole time!

00:10:57.240 --> 00:10:58.742 position:50% align:center
What if I throw it high?

00:10:58.825 --> 00:11:00.285 position:50% align:center
[MINATO] "Throw it high"?
What are you talking about?

00:11:00.368 --> 00:11:01.661 position:50% align:center
We'll use your vertical.

00:11:01.745 --> 00:11:03.621 position:50% align:center
You can jump higher
than all of them.

00:11:03.705 --> 00:11:05.373 position:50% align:center
[MINATO grunts]

00:11:05.457 --> 00:11:08.043 position:50% align:center
I've watched you for years;
I know that I'm right.

00:11:08.126 --> 00:11:09.794 position:50% align:center
They don't stand
a chance against you.

00:11:09.878 --> 00:11:12.464 position:50% align:center
I'll toss it above
and you jump for it!

00:11:17.052 --> 00:11:18.970 position:50% align:center
[whistle blows]

00:11:22.390 --> 00:11:24.267 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
Let's hope this works.

00:11:34.069 --> 00:11:35.236 position:50% align:center
[EITARO grunts]

00:11:35.320 --> 00:11:36.738 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:11:41.659 --> 00:11:43.119 position:50% align:center
[MINATO grunts]

00:11:49.417 --> 00:11:51.586 position:50% align:center
[TAKESHI]
No way!

00:11:51.670 --> 00:11:53.463 position:50% align:center
What a jump!

00:11:55.090 --> 00:11:56.841 position:50% align:center
[MINATO grunts]

00:11:58.009 --> 00:11:59.135 position:50% align:center
[KEITA, KOKI, MOMO gasp]

00:11:59.219 --> 00:12:00.387 position:50% align:center
[CHINU gasps]

00:12:00.470 --> 00:12:04.057 position:50% align:center
Go!

00:12:06.226 --> 00:12:10.021 position:50% align:center
Go!

00:12:11.189 --> 00:12:12.982 position:50% align:center
[grunts]

00:12:13.066 --> 00:12:13.733 position:50% align:center
[KEITA, KOKI gasp]

00:12:13.817 --> 00:12:16.486 position:50% align:center
[whistle blows]

00:12:24.160 --> 00:12:25.620 position:50% align:center
[MINATO]
I'm sorry.

00:12:26.663 --> 00:12:29.541 position:50% align:center
That pass was way better
than I expected it to be.

00:12:29.624 --> 00:12:36.589 position:50% align:center
Oh! Don't worry about it.

00:12:36.673 --> 00:12:39.009 position:50% align:center
[MINATO] Looks like
I underestimated everyone.

00:12:41.011 --> 00:12:44.848 position:50% align:center
[MINATO] Not just our opponents,
but my teammates, too.

00:12:49.394 --> 00:12:52.814 position:50% align:center
[MITAMURA] Don't worry team!
Y-You can turn this around!

00:12:55.275 --> 00:12:58.069 position:50% align:center
You've got a plan, right?
What'll you boys do?

00:12:58.153 --> 00:13:00.655 position:50% align:center
I dunno.

00:13:00.739 --> 00:13:04.200 position:50% align:center
Sorry, guys. Looks like
I failed you all as a captain.

00:13:06.369 --> 00:13:08.371 position:50% align:center
You've been blocking
tons of shots today.

00:13:08.455 --> 00:13:09.581 position:50% align:center
That's good enough.

00:13:09.664 --> 00:13:11.041 position:50% align:center
[GROUP gasps]

00:13:15.420 --> 00:13:16.963 position:50% align:center
Switch to offense, Ejiri.

00:13:17.047 --> 00:13:18.298 position:50% align:center
[TAKEKAZU]
Huh?

00:13:18.381 --> 00:13:20.467 position:50% align:center
Forget about me and take
the shot if you have one.

00:13:20.550 --> 00:13:22.093 position:50% align:center
If they leave the
middle open this half,

00:13:22.177 --> 00:13:24.512 position:50% align:center
we'll need to put
the pressure on them.

00:13:24.596 --> 00:13:26.973 position:50% align:center
It'll be my job to make
more space for you.

00:13:27.057 --> 00:13:28.516 position:50% align:center
But...

00:13:28.600 --> 00:13:31.478 position:50% align:center
You've got some serious throwing
power; better use it, right?

00:13:31.561 --> 00:13:34.105 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:13:34.189 --> 00:13:35.231 position:50% align:center
Damn straight.

00:13:35.315 --> 00:13:36.775 position:50% align:center
Well, he perked up.

00:13:36.858 --> 00:13:37.776 position:50% align:center
Can it!

00:13:37.859 --> 00:13:39.652 position:50% align:center
[BABAYARO,
