00:16:40.291 --> 00:16:41.209 position:50% align:center
[AKIHISA]
Three seconds!

00:16:41.292 --> 00:16:43.294 position:50% align:center
[TAKESHI grunts]

00:16:43.378 --> 00:16:45.922 position:50% align:center
[gasps, grunts]

