00:19:07.981 --> 00:19:09.607 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:19:09.691 --> 00:19:10.942 position:50% align:center
[EITARO]
What?

00:19:15.864 --> 00:19:17.699 position:50% align:center
Shoot it, Eitaro!

00:19:17.782 --> 00:19:18.700 position:50% align:center
