00:20:26.017 --> 00:20:29.145 position:50% align:center
[NORIMICHI]
No regrets here. I had fun.

00:20:31.272 --> 00:20:32.440 position:50% align:center
Come on, guys!

00:20:32.524 --> 00:20:34.734 position:50% align:center
Our match against
Shogaku's next!

00:20:34.818 --> 00:20:37.278 position:50% align:center
We'll win that one for sure!

00:20:40.907 --> 00:20:42.367 position:50% align:center
Definitely.

00:20:44.327 --> 00:20:46.538 position:50% align:center
